node.textContent: .range-slider .ngx-slider .ngx-slider-selection { background: rgb(0, 123, 255); }.range-slider .ngx-slider .ngx-slider-pointer { width: 16px; height: 16px; top: -6px; background-color: rgb(255, 193, 7); }.range-slider .ngx-slider .ngx-slider-pointer::after { top: 4px; left: 4px; background-color: rgb(0, 123, 255); }.range-slider .ngx-slider .ngx-slider-bubble { cursor: default; bottom: 12px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 6px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-size: small; }.switch[_ngcontent-vup-c70] { position: relative; display: inline-block; width: 56px; height: 20px; }.switch[_ngcontent-vup-c70] input[_ngcontent-vup-c70] { display: none; }.slider[_ngcontent-vup-c70] { position: absolute; cursor: pointer; inset: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 193, 7); transition: all 0.4s ease 0s; border-radius: 20px; }.slider[_ngcontent-vup-c70]::before { position: absolute; content: ""; height: 12px; width: 12px; left: 4px; bottom: 4px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); transition: all 0.4s ease 0s; border-radius: 50%; }input[_ngcontent-vup-c70]:checked + .slider[_ngcontent-vup-c70] { background-color: rgb(255, 193, 7); }input[_ngcontent-vup-c70]:focus + .slider[_ngcontent-vup-c70] { box-shadow: rgb(255, 193, 7) 0px 0px 1px; }input[_ngcontent-vup-c70]:checked + .slider[_ngcontent-vup-c70]::before { transform: translate(36px); }.slider[_ngcontent-vup-c70]::after { content: "And"; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); display: block; position: absolute; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); top: 50%; left: 50%; font-size: x-small; font-weight: 700; }input[_ngcontent-vup-c70]:checked + .slider[_ngcontent-vup-c70]::after { content: "Or"; }
